    <p>{`I thought I’d share a few web technologies that I’ve been playing around with recently as well as some that I am hoping to learn more about.`}</p>
    <p>{`As the `}<g class="gr_ gr_3 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim ContextualSpelling ins-del" data-gr-id="3" id="3">{`back-bone`}</g>{` of a lot of hobby-projects I’ve been working on recently has been `}<a parentName="p" {...{
